an style=\"display: block; font-size: 0.98rem; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: #3b4b5c;\">SCORCHED PEANUT BAR 45G</span><span style=\"display: block; margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #6bb6d9;\">$3.99</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </aside>\n<h2>Where to find Scorched Peanut Bars?</h2>\n\n<p>Kards &amp; Kandy all stores in Newcastle stock it. For those looking to buy multiple bars or wanting to combine them with other treats, you can find a full range of <a href=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/where-to-buy/bulk-lollies-australia/\">bulk lollies in Australia</a> at our online store, making it easy to get everything you need in one place.</p>\n\n<p>For collectors of vintage and comeback sweets, Scorched Peanut Bars sit alongside other iconic Australian chocolate bars. Check out our guide to <a href=\"https://sweetsworld.com.au/candy-guides/best-candy-australia-2026/\">the best candy in Australia 2026</a> to discover other must-try treats that might interest you.</p>\n\n<section class=\"ai-faq-block\" style=\"margin-top:40px\">\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<details style=\"margin-bottom:18px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:6px\">\n<summary style=\"padding:16px 18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.6\">How long have Scorched Peanut Bars been unavailable?</summary>\n<div style=\"padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8\">Scorched Peanut Bars were off the shelves for 40 years before being relaunched by Cooks Confectionery. This classic Australian chocolate bar has made a triumphant return to delight nostalgic sweet lovers.</div>\n</details>\n<details style=\"margin-bottom:18px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:6px\">\n<summary style=\"padding:16px 18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.6\">What exactly is in a Scorched Peanut Bar?</summary>\n<div style=\"padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8\">Scorched Peanut Bars feature scorched peanuts in caramelised toffee, all wrapped in a rich chocolate coating. It&#x27;s a delicious combination of textures and flavours that made the original bar so beloved.</div>\n</details>\n<details style=\"margin-bottom:18px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:6px\">\n<summary style=\"padding:16px 18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.6\">Can I buy Scorched Peanut Bars online?</summary>\n<div style=\"padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8\">Yes, you can purchase Scorched Peanut Bars online at the Sweetsworld store. They&#x27;re also available in physical locations at Kards &amp; Kandy stores in Charlestown Square, Westfield Kotara, and Stockland Greenhills.</div>\n</details>\n<details style=\"margin-bottom:18px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:6px\">\n<summary style=\"padding:16px 18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.6\">Would Scorched Peanut Bars make a good gift?</summary>\n<div style=\"padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8\">Absolutely! Since these are a nostalgic favourite that&#x27;s been unavailable for decades, they make an excellent gift for anyone who remembers and loves the original bar. Sweetsworld also offers candy gift box options that could include these bars for friends and family.</div>\n</details>\n<details style=\"margin-bottom:18px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:6px\">\n<summary style=\"padding:16px 18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.6\">Has the recipe changed since the original Scorched Peanut Bar?</summary>\n<div style=\"padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8\">While the page mentions the bar is &quot;back and better than ever,&quot; the core recipe remains true to the original with scorched peanuts in caramelised toffee and chocolate coating. Customer reviews confirm they taste just as good as fans remember!</div>\n</details>\n</section>\n\n<!-- AI_SLOT:SCHEMA -->\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n  \"mainEntity\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Ho